(6, 'service', 6, '<div class="Section1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b><font color="#0000FF">আমাদের সেবাসমূহঃ<span style="mso-ansi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN" lang="AR-SA"></span></span></font></b><br></div><div class="Section1">\n\n<br></div><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:NikoshBAN;\nmso-bidi-language:BN-BD"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">1.<span style="font:7.0pt ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:\nNikoshBAN;mso-bidi-language:BN-BD" lang="BN-BD">সমবায় সদস্যগণকে সমবায় ব্যবস্থাপনা ও দক্ষতা\nউন্নয়ন বিষয়ক প্রশিক্ষণ প্রদান করা। </span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:NikoshBAN;\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">2.<span style="font:7.0pt ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:\nNikoshBAN;mso-bidi-language:BN-BD" lang="BN-BD">সমবায় সদস্যগণকে আয়বর্ধনমূলক (আইজিএ)\nপ্রশিক্ষণ প্রদানের মাধ্যমে উদ্যোক্তা সৃষ্টি করা।</span><span style="font-size:\n13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:NikoshBAN;\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">3.<span style="font:7.0pt ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:\nNikoshBAN;mso-bidi-language:BN-BD" lang="BN-BD">সমবায় বিভাগের কর্মকর্তা-কর্মচারিদের পেশাগত </span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:NikoshBAN;\nmso-bidi-language:BN-BD">দক্ষতা<span lang="BN-BD"> উন্নয়নে প্রশিক্ষণ প্রদান করা।</span></span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:"></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:NikoshBAN;\nmso-bidi-font-weight:bold"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">4.<span style="font:7.0pt ">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:\nNikoshBAN;mso-bidi-language:BN-BD" lang="BN-BD">সমবায় উন্নয়ন ও প্রসারে গবেষণা ও প্রকাশনা\nকার্যক্রম পরিচালনা করা।</span> <br></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo3">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b><font color="#0000FF">আমাদের <span style="mso-ansi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-size:13.0pt;\nfont-family:NikoshBAN;mso-bidi-language:BN" lang="BN">কৌশলগত</span></span><span style="mso-ansi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-size:13.0pt;\nfont-family:NikoshBAN" lang="BN"> </span></span><span style="mso-ansi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-bidi-language:BN" lang="BN">উদ্দেশ্যসমূহ</span></span><span style="mso-ansi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-size:13.0pt;\nfont-family:NikoshBAN" lang="BN"> </span></span><span style="mso-ansi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN" lang="AR-SA">(Strategic Objectives):</span></span></font></b></p><div class="Section1"><b style="mso-ansi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN" lang="AR-SA"></span></b><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:NikoshBAN;\nmso-bidi-language:BN-BD"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">1.<span style="font:7.0pt " times="" new="" roman""="">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:\nNikoshBAN;mso-bidi-language:BN-BD" lang="BN-BD">প্রশিক্ষণার্থীগণকে </span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:NikoshBAN;\nmso-bidi-language:BN-BD">দক্ষতা<span lang="BN-BD">বৃদ্ধি ও আয়বর্ধনমূলক<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>(আইজিএ)<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;\n</span>প্রশিক্ষণ প্রদান করে দক্ষ মানব সম্পদে রূপান্তর।</span></span></p>\n\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:NikoshBAN;\nmso-bidi-language:BN-BD"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">2.<span style="font:7.0pt " times="" new="" roman""="">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:\nNikoshBAN;mso-bidi-language:BN-BD" lang="BN-BD">বাংলাদেশ সমবায় একাডেমীকে সৃজনশীল ও যুগোপযোগী\nপ্রশিক্ষণ প্রতিষ্ঠান হিসেবে গড়ে তোলা।</span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;\nfont-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-bidi-language:BN-BD"></span><span style="font-size:13.0pt;font-family:NikoshBAN;mso-fareast-font-family:" times="" new="" roman";="" mso-bidi-language:bn-bd"=""><br></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left:.25in;text-align:justify;text-justify:\ninter-ideograph;text-indent:-.25in;mso-l